\mt1 Revelesen  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip Jon in aposol riti s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo. N…ôp…®n k…®n…ôrhi irapw in rev…ôn fwe t…ôn…ô …ômwer…®s riti n…ô…°h…®n n…ô Patmos n…ôn…ô m…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i Revelesen. Jon rokeikei m…ô truvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me s…ôm…ôme kamo n…ômis…ôien m…®nraha t…® nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha ia Iesu Kristo. Jon rokeikei m…ô nakalasia me tuh…ôukur…ôn m…ô Kumwes…ôn ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia n…ôfe kamo ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i. Ia n…ôkuku…ô i N…ôn…®mw…®n ram…ô…°kiari mamo s…ôukur…ôn m…ô Iesu Kristo in I…ôr…®m…ônu. In ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia n…ôrmama me pam m…®ne narimnari me pam, mam…ôr…®m…ônu mwi ia n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme ham…ôuvehi n…®skaiien asori ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i. Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama m…®ne Setan ia kwopun napw rau…ôk ik…®n. Kumwes…ôn tro n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô in ram…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô trier irapw. In tro mwi neiai vi riti m…®ne t…®pr…ôn…ô vi riti.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rakupw…ôn  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Dan 2:28-29, Rev 1:19, 22:6\x*N…ôkuku…ô i ram…ô…°kiari ia nari m nari me s…ôm…ôme Iesu Kristo r…®no pui. Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen narimnari me i min m…ô in trahat…ôn s…ôv…ônhi iotukwininari me ir…ô pw…ôh ir…ôha h…ôtoni mh…ôukur…ôn narimnari me n…ôha r…®pko mh…ô tui tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôier pehe. Iesu r…ôrhi pen a…°elo s…ôv…ônhi rev…ôn m…ôvisau pen narimnari me i m s…ôv…ônhi iotukwininari riti n…ô…°h…®n n…ô Jon.  
\v 2 Jon n…ô r…®rai pen ia n…ôkuku…ô i narimnari me pam s…ô in r…®n…ôtoni. In i n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn m…®ne n…ô…°kiariien s…ô Iesu Kristo r…®ni m…ô ro n…®p…ôrhienien.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Rev 22:7,10\x*Pw…ôh Kumwes…ôn r…ôkwein amasan ia i…ôrmama s…ô tr…ôvsini irapw n…ô…°kiariien me ia n…ôkuku…ô i. Pw…ôh in r…ôkwein amasan mwi ia s…ôm…ôme tuh…ôre…°i mhesi pen n…ôfe k…®m…ôrai pen ia n…ôkuku…ô i. Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n s…ô narimnari me i tuh…ôier pehe ir…ô ruv…ôuvehe ipaka.   
\s1 Jon r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me ia taon me n…ôha sefen ia profens Esia  
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Eks 3:14-15, Rev 1:8, 3:1, Rev 4:5,8, 5:6, Rev 11:17, 16:5, Aes 11:2\x*Iou Jon iakamrai n…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha nakalasia me ia taon me n…ôha sefen ia profens Esia. Iak…ôfwaki m…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ô r…®nar…ô fwe kupw…ôn, mar…ô ipwet m…®ne, mamev…ôn meste tr…®pkiw…ôn mh…ô, in truvei pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha. Iak…ôfwaki m…ô n…ôn…®mw…®n me n…ôha sefen kupw…ôn ia jea s…ô in ram…ôkure ir…ô mam…ôr…®m…ônu,  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Jon 18:37, Kol 1:18, Sam 89:27, Rev 3:14, 17:14, 1Jon 1:7, 4:10\x*m…®ne Iesu Kristo ir…ôha mwi tuho iam…®nhi ir…ô. Iesu Kristo in i…ôrmama i r…®m…ôni irapw n…ôfe in r…®n…ôtoni m…®re…°i n…ôrmama h…ôukur…ôn n…ôt…®…°iteien ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi. In i…ôrmama i r…®m…ôkupw…ôn m…ôtui ia n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme h…ôuvamh…ô. In i…ôrmama i ram…ôr…®m…ônu ia ki…° me s…ôv…ôi t…®pr…ôn…ô i. In ramokeikei k…®taha, muvi n…®ten meivinari ia k…®taha ir…ô m…ô noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®taha ko h…ôpk…ôkwt…ômhiri mh…ô mwi k…®taha.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1Tes 2:5,9, Rev 5:10, 20:6\x*In ro k…®taha s…ômwhen ia ki…° me m…®ne pris me ia n…ômri Tata Kumwes…ôn s…ôv…ônhi. Pw…ôh nasoriien m…®ne n…ôr…®m…ônuien krauev…ôn tukwe in ia nuk nuk me. Ou…ôh pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   
\q1
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Mat 24:30, Jon 19:34-37\x*H…ôt…ô ro. In rauvehe ia reri n…ôpu…ô me.  
\q2 N…ôrmama me pam tuh…ôtoni in ia n…ônimenraha.  
\q1 Ir…ôha s…ôm…ôme h…ôn…ôpi in ia nitei,  
\q2 m…®ne n…ôrmama ia kw…ôn…ôkwus me pam ia t…ôkure t…®pr…ôn…ô i tuh…ôtoni,  
\q2 rer…®nraha r…ôpou has…ôk tukwe.  
