\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Dan 7:13, 10:5\x*Ia kurkwanraha i…ôrmama riti r…ômwhen ia i…ôm…ôti i…ôrmama riti. T…®nari s…ôv…ônhi r…ôpw…ômw…®s. R…ôkwani nari k…®no ia kol rukurau ia kw…ônpwenh…®n.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Dan 7:9, 10:6, Rev 2:18, 19:12, Rev 14:2\x*N…®mwai nukw…ônen r…ôpsan r…ômwhen ia n…®mwheri sipsip. R…ôpsan p…®k r…ômwhen ia n…®s…ôkwai t…ôsi.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Kris ram…®ni iam…®nhi ir…ô m…®nu…ô ‚ÄúR…ôpsan p…®k r…ômwhen ia sno.‚Äù\f* N…ônimen mi krou…ômwhen ia n…ôrami napw.  
\v 15 N…®sun mi krauser rou…ômwhen ia aean n…ôha prons s…ô kuvani ia napw m…ô s…ô r…ôr…ôha traiu raka. Rer…®n r…ômwhen ia nui asori s…ô ramiv…ô mamier…®…°.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Hip 4:12, Rev 1:20, Rev 2:12,16, Rev 19:15,21\x*In rauvehi k…ôm…ôhau me sefen ia r…ô…°…®n mwatuk. Nau s…ôv…ôi narua…°…ônien r…ôhi…ô ia n…®karen mi ruku pen ia n…®p…ô…°i n…ôkwan mier. N…ônimen r…ômwhen ia meri s…ô ram…ôhiapw ia rukw…ôsik…ôr.   
\p
\v 17 N…ôp…®n iak…ôtoni i…ôm…ô n…ôha iakmwei irapw ia n…®sun mi r…ômwhen iakemh…ô. M…ôt…ô in r…ômri pehe r…ô…°…®n mwatuk ia nirak, m…®ni m…ô, ‚ÄúTik…ôpw…ôh nehek…®rien. Iou i…ôrmama i iak…®nar…ô raka kupw…ôn, n…ôn…ô takar…ô mwi kurir…ô.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Aes 44:6, 48:12, Rev 2:8, 22:13\x*Iou i…ôrmama i iakam…®ru. Fwe kupw…ôn iak…®mamh…ô, m…ôt…ô …ôt…ô ro t…ôkwt…ôkwuni iakuv…ôm…®ru tak…®m…®ru ia nuk nuk me. Iou iakasori ia Noien I…ôrmama Remh…ô, masori mwi ia Imwei N…ôkur H…ôuvamh…ô.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Kris ram…®ni iam…®nhi ir…ô m…®nu…ô ‚ÄúIou iakauvehi ki me s…ôv…ôi Noien I…ôrmama Remh…ô m…®ne Imwei N…ôkur H…ôuvamh…ô.‚Äù\f*   
\p
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Rev 1:1\x*Ro pen tikam…ôkeikei m…®rai pen ia n…ôkuku…ô narimnari me i ikam…ôtoni, s…ôm…ôme kamo ipwet m…®ne, m…®ne s…ôm…ôme tuh…ôuvehe kurir…ô.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Rev 1:16, 2:1, Rev 3:1\x*Tak…®ni pehe tukw ik i n…®pwrai k…ôm…ôhau me i ir…ôha pam sefen ikam…ôt…ô ia r…ô…°…®k mwatuk m…®ne n…®pwrai n…ôri laet ram…ôkure ut…ô ir…ô ir…ôha pam sefen k…®no ia kol. K…ôm…ôhau me n…ôha sefen ir…ôha n…ôha na…°elo me s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me s…ôm…ôme kamhar…ô ia taon me n…ôha sefen. N…ôn…ô n…ôri laet ram…ôkure ut…ô ir…ô ir…ôha pam sefen k…®no ia kol ir…ôha n…ôha nakalasia me s…ôm…ôme kamhar…ô ia taon me n…ôha sefen.‚Äù   
\c 2  
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien ramev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe Efesas  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Rev 1:16; 20\x*‚ÄúRai n…ôkuku…ô riti rev…ôn t…® a…°elo s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me ia taon n…ôha Efesas, m…®ni pen m…®nu…ô:\fig Nakalasia me ia taon me n…ôha sefen|alt="The seven churches" src="7 churches [S Tanna].tif" size="col" loc="Rev 2:1" copy="SIL" ref="Rev 1:11" \fig*  
\pi1 N…ô…°kiariien i s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama s…ô rauvehi k…ôm…ôhau sefen ia r…ô…°…®n mwatuk, n…ôn…ô, mamav…ôn ia kurkwai n…ôri laet ram…ôkure ut…ô ir…ô ir…ôha pam sefen k…®no ia kol.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Rev 2:19, Rev 3:1,8,15, 1Jon 4:1\x*Iou iakukur…ôn noien me s…ôk…®miaha. Iakukur…ôn m…ô hiam…ômwur p…®k mamh…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia n…ôp…®n me. Iakukur…ôn m…ô hiam…ôr…ôpinh…ô ia n…ôkur …ôr…ôha. Hi…ôn…ôkiri noien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me n…ôha kamh…ôni m…ô ir…ôha aposol me m…ôt…ô r…®pko mh…ô ir…ôha p…ôrhien, n…ôn…ô, hi…ôn…ôtoni raka m…ô ir…ôha kamheiku…ô.  
\v 3 Iakukur…ôn m…ô ia n…ôp…®n me kamo n…ômis…ôien m k…®miaha t…® n…ô…°h…®k, m…ôt…ô hiam…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôpouien.   
\pi1
\v 4 M…ôt…ô nari riti n…ôha ik…®n hiamo r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô ia n…ônimek. K…®miaha hi…ôn…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien kupw…ôn s…ôk…®miaha.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Rev 2:16,22, Rev 3:3,19\x*Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô rer…®miaha tramrhi n…ôrerien s…ô hi…ôn…ôrer ir…ô fwe kupw…ôn kurir…ô hi…ômwei. Tih…ôr…ôr…®…° ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®miaha, mho narimnari me n…ôha s…ô hi…ônamo fwe kupw…ôn. Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô hi…ôpw…ôh n…®r…ôr…®…°ien ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®miaha, n…ôn…ô takuvehe tukumiaha muvehi raka s…ôk…®miaha n…ôri laet ram…ôkure ut…ô ir…ô ia t…ômwhek…®n.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Sam 139:21\x*M…ôt…ô nari kuatia n…ôha ik…®n hiamo ramasan. K…®miaha hi…ômw…ôki noien me n…ôha n…ôrmama s…ôv…ôi Nikolas kamho r…ômwhen iou mwi iak…ômw…ôki.   
\pi1
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jen 2:9, Rev 22:2,14,19\x*I…ôrmama s…ô n…ôkw…ôre…°…®n rar…ô tram…ôkeikei m…ôt…ôr…®…° amasan ia n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôm…ôme N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan rani pen t…® nakalasia me. I…ôrmama s…ô tr…®skai meste narua…°…ônien rukurau, iou tak…ôseni in r…ôni nukwai nei kauvehi n…®m…®ruien ir…ô ram…ôrer ia kwopun n…ôha Parataes s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.‚Äù   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien ramev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe Smana  
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Rev 1:17\x*‚ÄúRai n…ôkuku…ô riti rev…ôn t…® a…°elo s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me ia taon n…ôha Smana, m…®ni pen m…®nu…ô:  
\pi1 N…ô…°kiariien i s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama s…ô r…®nar…ô raka kupw…ôn, n…ôn…ô trar…ô mwi kurir…ô. In remh…ô m…ôtui mwi.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 2Kor 11:14-15, Jem 2:5, Rev 3:9\x*Iou iakukur…ôn n…ômis…ôien s…ôk…®miaha. Iakukur…ôn m…ô s…ôk…®miaha naut…ô riw…ôn. (M…ôt…ô ia n…ônimek naut…ô s…ôk…®miaha rasori anan.) Iakukur…ôn n…ô…°kiariien …ôr…ôha me n…ôha n…ôrmama nepw…®n kamh…ôni ia k…®miaha. Ir…ôha kamh…ôni m…ô ir…ôha n…ôkur Isrel, m…ôt…ô rek…ôm. Nous…ôs…®mw…®nien s…ôv…ônraha s…ôv…ôi Setan.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Mat 10:28, 2Tim 4:8, Jem 1:12, Rev 3:11\x*Tih…ôpw…ôh nehek…®rien n…ômis…ôien i tr…®pko mh…ô tui reste k…®miaha. H…ôre…°i ro. Setan tr…®pkos…ô pen k…®miaha nepw…®n ia kalapus m…ô tro m…ôt…ô sas ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha. Tih…ôre…°i n…ômis…ôien ia n…ôp…®n me i ir…ôha pam ten. K…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôrer …ôknek…®n n…ôri au…ôr a tr…®ni m…®nu…ô kousi …ôpune k…®miaha, n…ôn…ô iou takuvei pehe n…®m…®ruien m k…®miaha r…ômwhen k…ôf…ôfau pen k…ôf…ôfau amasan ia k…ônkapw…ô i…ôrmama s…ô r…ôvt…ônhi n…ôrmama ia naiuien.   
\pi1
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Rev 20:14, 21:8\x*I…ôrmama s…ô n…ôkw…ôre…°…®n rar…ô tram…ôkeikei m…ôt…ôr…®…° amasan ia n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôm…ôme N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan rani pen t…® nakalasia me. I…ôrmama s…ô tr…®skai meste narua…°…ônien rukurau in tr…ôpw…ôh nemh…ôien ia nemh…ôien s…ô ro k…ôru ir…ô.‚Äù   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien ramev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe Pekamam  
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Aes 49:2, Rev 1:16\x*‚ÄúRai n…ôkuku…ô riti rev…ôn t…® a…°elo s…ôv…ôi nakalasia me ia taon n…ôha Pekamam, m…®ni pen m…®nu…ô:  
\pi1 N…ô…°kiariien i s…ôv…ôi i…ôrmama s…ô rauvehi nau s…ôv…ôi narua…°…ônien r…ôhi…ô ia n…®karen p…ôri mi.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Rev 3:8\x*Iou iakukur…ôn kwopun hiamar…ô ik…®n. Jea s…ô Setan ram…ôkure ir…ô mam…ôr…®m…ônu in n…ôha ia kwopun n…ôha, m…ôt…ô k…®miaha hiamuvehi …ôknek…®n n…ô…°h…®k ia n…ôp…®n me, mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôrkwaf…ôien i m…ô hiamahat…ôt…ô ia nirak. P…ôrhien hi…ôpw…ôh mwi n…ôrkwaf…ôien i fwe kupw…ôn n…ôp…®n Antipas ramar…ô ihi. In i…ôrmama riti s…ôiou iakukur…ôn n…ôt…®…°iteien ir…ô. R…®n…ôrer irapw m…ô…°kiari ia nirak kousi …ôpune in ia taon s…ôk…®miaha, kwopun Setan ramar…ô ik…®n.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Nam 22-24, Nam 25:1-2, Nam 31:16, 2Tes 2:15\x*M…ôt…ô narimnari me nepw…®n n…ôha ik…®n hiamo h…ôpkatukwatukw mh…ô ia n…ônimek. K…®miaha me nepw…®n kamh…ôkurir…ô nahat…ônien s…ôv…ôi Palam. Palam n…ôha in r…®nahat…ôn Ki…° Palak m…ô in tr…ôrhi…ôrhi n…ôkur Isrel pw…ôh ir…ôha ho noien …ôr…ôha, mhani n…ôve…°…®nien s…ô k…®m…ôuvei pen m n…ôn…®mwi nari me s…ô kam…ôfwaki pen m…®nraha, n…ôn…ô, mh…ôiri …ôpnapen ir…ôha me.  
\v 15 Ia noien n…ôha k…®miaha nepw…®n mwi kamh…ôkurir…ô nahat…ônien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi Nikolas.  
